    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">A bingo — using all seven tiles for a 50-point bonus — is the single biggest scoring opportunity in Scrabble. But finding one under time pressure requires more than vocabulary. You need a system for quickly assessing bingo potential and techniques to extract the word when it exists.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">The Quick Assessment — Does This Rack Have Potential?</h2>

    <p>Before spending clock time searching, run a 5-second assessment. Not every rack deserves bingo attention — some are clearly better played as shorter words.</p>

    <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
