      <p class="text-base text-gray-200 mt-1"><span class="text-white font-medium">2. Duplicates:</span> No duplicate tiles = better. Two of the same cuts options significantly.</p>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-200 mt-1"><span class="text-white font-medium">3. Stem present:</span> Can you see 5-6 letters of SATIRE, RETINA, or INSERT? Hunt hard.</p>
