    <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">The 6+1 Method — Systematic Stem Scanning</h2>

    <p>The most reliable technique is the 6+1 method. Instead of anagramming all seven tiles at once, identify a six-letter stem you know, then check whether the seventh tile completes a valid word.</p>

